cleaned_text: VacTrAK *Influenz a vaccine supplied by the state of Alaska **MedImmune is a subsidiary of AstraZeneca ***ID Biomedical is part of GlaxoSmithKline If your practice manages private vaccine inventory in VacTrAK, make sure the vaccine names and types you enter into inventory match the administered vaccine. Speak with the person entering your lot numbers if you notice any issues/problems. Refer to the CDC reference tables for the most up to date CVX - vaccine codes and MVX - manufacturer codes required for data exchange between VacTrAK and electronic health record systems. CDC reference tables for NDC codes and Vaccine Price Lists are also available.
